Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Pasay Road Extending from the Municipality of Makati to Pasay City Both in Metropolitan Manila, to Antonio S. Arnaiz Avenue
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 783
An Act Changing the Name of the Pasay Road Extending from the Municipality of Makati to Pasay City Both in Metropolitan Manila, to Antonio S. Arnaiz Avenue
Section 1. The name of Pasay Road extending from the Fort-Bonifacio Road (station 12.820) in the Municipality of Makati, to Roxas Boulevard-Libertad intersection (station 4.330) in Pasay City both in Metropolitan Manila, is changed to Antonio S. Arnaiz Avenue.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
